es":[1244,7020,494,1555,11059,1006,4755,9509,564,36911],"slug":"virtua-fighter-5-final-showdown","summary":"The fifth entry in SEGA's fighting game series. Once again, the real-time level of visual detail and character animation has been upped to the most advanced levels, with next-generation lighting and detail on the fighters and environments. Players will be able to customize their characters by selecting from various patterned costumes and a wide range of attachable items that can be placed onto each fighter's various body parts. Players will not only achieve victory by defeating highly-skilled opponents, but will also compete for prizes and earn in-game money through the match to buy many items at an in-game shop.\n\nVirtua Fighter 5: Final Showdown contains a full overhaul of Virtua Fighter 5's mechanics, balance and animations, along with new game modes, new dynamic fighting arenas, a massive collection of customizable character items and new characters.","total_rating":85.70920949204427,"total_rating_count":21,"url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/virtua-fighter-5-final-showdown","videos":[{"id":49666,"video_id":"hGNMcif9RjA"}],"websites":[{"id":125117,"url":"https://virtuafighter.fandom.com/wiki/Virtua_Fighter_5_Final_Showdown","type":{"id":2,"type":"Community Wiki"}},{"id":335170,"url":"https://www.twitch.tv/directory/game/Virtua%20Fighter%205%20Final%20Showdown","type":{"id":6,"type":"Twitch"}},{"id":607877,"url":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Virtua_Fighter_5","type":{"id":3,"type":"Wikipedia"}}]}